title: A War Without Weapons
tags: adlib Dream electronic OPL3 Piano RobertMiles trance
info:
Allready the 5th Trance-Dream hits from Cyborg Jeff in one week. Rhythm of great productions was growing fast ! In this new song, I once again mixed piano’s melody as in Robert Miles songs with here a second voices using an electronic instrument close to the Adlib FM sounds of the Yamaha OPL3 that we could hear in the MS-DOS PC version of the game Nicky Boom…. Some sounds was also sampled out of Waxattack and Ice Mc titles.
This flying melodies, i re-try to work on it many times. The best version was an update of this one in 1997 that you could hear in the anniversary album « We Want More« .
A war witout weapons…. with only musical notes….
